[I] Framebuffer Doom

[T] fbDOOM is an adaptation of the original DOOM to be easily portable to
[T] framebuffer devices with minimal depenencies.

[U] https://github.com/maximevince/fbDOOM

[A] Maxime Vincent
[M] foxdrodd

[C] extra/game
[F] CROSS

[L] OpenSource
[V] 1728016

[E] add libsdl

[D] 6baa208be7cf9f3f2e60a57b1ab0f6e5527b02b4e9b7f68e34987c3f fbDOOM-1728016.tar.gz https://github.com/maximevince/fbDOOM/archive/1728016/

srcdir=fbDOOM*/fbdoom/
makeinstopt=
var_append GCC_WRAPPER_APPEND ' ' -std=gnu11
hook_add postmake 5 'install fbdoom $root$bindir/'
